videos.headline: Nebraska opens up scoring with Newby 8-yard TD
videos.description: Nebraska RB Terrell Newby makes his way into the end zone for an 8-yard touchdown to give the Cornhuskers the lead over Maryland.

videos.headline: Newby extends Nebraska's lead with second rushing TD
videos.description: Nebraska RB Terrell Newby rushes right and into the end zone for his second rushing touchdown of the day against Maryland.

videos.headline: Spencer Lindsay 32 yd FG blocked by JC Jackson
videos.description: Spencer Lindsay 32 yd FG BLOCKED blocked by JC Jackson

videos.headline: Armstrong, Nebraska pay tribute to Foltz
videos.description: Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong lays flowers on top of the jersey of Sam Foltz, paying tribute to his former teammate who died over the summer.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Armstrong, Nebraska pay tribute to Foltz) 2016/11/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maryland WR zips around Nebraska defense for 92-yard TD
videos.description: Maryland WR D.J. Moore catches a pass and scampers evasively around Nebraska's defense, racing downfield 92 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: 8-year-old's wish to become a Cornhusker is granted
videos.description: Eight-year-old Jack Johnson, born with a genetic disorder, gets the opportunity to run out on to the field with Nebraska and join the captains for the coin toss.
